      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it doesn't feel like a space i can just rest in though. even when i'm alone, i'm just thinking about what they're saying. it feels like there's no way out of the cycle. like no matter what i do, the noise just follows me. it feels like the only way to actually get away from it all is to just... stop. do you think it's weird that i feel that way?",
